# зависимость сумм квадратов расстояний от числа кластеров
sse = []
k_list = range(1, 31)
for k in k_list:
    km = KMeans(n_clusters = k, init = 'random', n_init = 10, max_iter = 100, tol = 0.0001, random_state = 0)
    km.fit(data[["latitude", "longitude"]])
    sse.append(km.inertia_)
sse_km = pd.DataFrame({'SSE': sse, 'n_clusters': list(k_list)})

sns.set(font_scale = 1.5)
f, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(15, 5))
ax.set_xticks(range(1, 31, 1))
sns.lineplot(data = sse_km, x = "n_clusters", y = "SSE", marker = 'o');

# отбор информативных признаков
def select_feature(model, data, label, l, plot_flag = True):
  res_f1 = []
  for i in l:
    select_k_best_classifier = SelectKBest(mutual_info_classif, k = i)
    X_new = select_k_best_classifier.fit_transform(data, label)
    X_new = pd.DataFrame(X_new)

    skf = KFold(n_splits = 5)
    f1 = []
    for train_index, test_index in skf.split(label):
      X_t = X_new.iloc[train_index]
      X_v = X_new.iloc[test_index]
      y_t = label.iloc[train_index]
      y_v = label.iloc[test_index]


      model.fit(X_t, y_t)
      preds = model.predict(X_t)
      f1.append(f1_score(y_t, preds, average='weighted'))

    res_f1.append(np.mean(f1))
  feature_f1 = pd.DataFrame({'count_feature': l, 'f1': res_f1})

  if(plot_flag):
    sns.set(font_scale = 1.5)
    f, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(15, 5))
    ax.set_xticks(range(2, 31, 2))
    sns.lineplot(data = feature_f1, x = "count_feature", y = "f1");

  kbest = feature_f1[feature_f1['f1'] == feature_f1.f1.max()].count_feature.reset_index(drop = True)

  return(kbest[0])
In [142]:
def n_best(train, test, label, n):
  select_k_best_classifier = SelectKBest(score_func = mutual_info_classif, k = n)
  print(select_k_best_classifier)
  train_best = select_k_best_classifier.fit_transform(train, label)
  train_best = pd.DataFrame(train_best, columns = list(train.columns[select_k_best_classifier.get_support()]))

  test_best = select_k_best_classifier.transform(test)
  test_best = pd.DataFrame(test_best, columns = list(test.columns[select_k_best_classifier.get_support()]))

  return(train_best, test_best)

# ROC-кривые
fpr_rf, tpr_rf, _ = metrics. roc_curve (Y_test, pred_rf)
auc_rf = metrics. roc_auc_score (Y_test, pred_rf)
fpr_knn, tpr_knn, _ = metrics. roc_curve (Y_test, pred_knn)
auc_knn = metrics. roc_auc_score (Y_test, pred_knn)
fpr_svm, tpr_svm, _ = metrics. roc_curve (Y_test, pred_svm)
auc_svm = metrics. roc_auc_score (Y_test, pred_svm)

plt.plot (fpr_rf,tpr_rf, label=" AUC_RF = "+str(auc_rf))
plt.plot (fpr_knn,tpr_knn,label=" AUC_KNN = "+str(auc_knn))
plt.plot (fpr_svm,tpr_svm,label=" AUC_SVM = "+str(auc_svm))
plt.ylabel('True Positive Rate')
plt.xlabel('False Positive Rate')
plt.legend(loc=4)
plt.show()

различия между моделями, обученными методом опорных векторов и методом к-ближайших соседа, незначительны. однако, проанализировав результаты, можно увидеть, что лучшая классификация - метод опорных векторов. классификация методом случайного леса самая худшая
